     Run directly
     cd "H:\This\This\My APP\Bookofshadow\bookofprompt"
     flutter pub get
     flutter run

Build and run
          Clean flutter
               flutter clean
          Build .exe ( with other files)
               flutter build windows --release
     Build one .exe using Enigma ( run right away)
                Enigma Virtual Box 
     Build one .exe using inno setup
               cd .. && "C:\Program Files (x86)\Inno Setup 6\ISCC.exe" create_installer.iss
     Build a portable zip
               # Save this as "Create_Portable.ps1" and run it
               cd "H:\This\This\My APP\Bookofshadow"; cd bookofprompt; flutter clean; flutter build windows --release; cd ..\Installer; Remove-Item "PromptManager_Portable_v1.0.2" -Recurse -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; New-Item -ItemType Directory -Name "PromptManager_Portable_v1.0.2" -Force; Copy-Item "..\bookofprompt\build\windows\x64\runner\Release\*" "PromptManager_Portable_v1.0.2\" -Recurse -Force; New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path "PromptManager_Portable_v1.0.2\data" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; Compress-Archive -Path "PromptManager_Portable_v1.0.2" -DestinationPath "PromptManager_Portable_v1.0.2.zip" -Force; Write-Host "✅ Portable package created!" -ForegroundColor Green
